00:56:41,439 --> 00:56:43,441
MS. KANG

731
00:56:44,067 --> 00:56:44,984
Hello?

732
00:56:45,777 --> 00:56:48,321
No. I said I was going to Seosan.

733
00:56:48,863 --> 00:56:50,365
I'm on my way. Why?

734
00:56:51,574 --> 00:56:53,201
What was posted?

735
00:56:54,786 --> 00:56:55,829
Send it to me.

