00:57:16,224 --> 00:57:17,475
The hospital.

740
00:57:17,559 --> 00:57:19,477
-Pardon?
-Go to the hospital in Hanseong.

741
00:57:20,812 --> 00:57:22,147
Right now?

742
00:57:22,230 --> 00:57:24,774
GLUTTON

743
00:57:47,172 --> 00:57:48,631
Okay.

744
00:57:54,762 --> 00:57:57,599
Are you still doing the reduction?
What's taking so long?

745
00:57:57,682 --> 00:57:59,809
Lazy bums. We're so busy.

746
00:58:02,270 --> 00:58:03,771
My goodness.

747
00:58:12,614 --> 00:58:14,032
-Deputy Director Kim.
-Yes?

748
00:58:14,115 --> 00:58:16,868
There's a post on the portal.
I think you should take a look.

