so there are no cameras.

759
00:59:37,740 --> 00:59:39,826
I got the footage of the hallway instead.

760
00:59:40,368 --> 00:59:41,744
Whose ID was it?

761
00:59:41,828 --> 00:59:43,204
Well, it was…

762
00:59:44,247 --> 00:59:46,291
Lee Bo-hun's. The late hospital director.

763
00:59:54,507 --> 00:59:56,009
How did they get this?

764
00:59:56,718 --> 00:59:59,971
Can anyone access the entire hospital's
profit and loss statements?

765
01:00:00,054 --> 01:00:04,475
No. The chiefs get monthly reports,
but only for their own departments.

766
01:00:04,559 --> 01:00:06,060
Previously, the foundation chairperson

767
01:00:06,144 --> 01:00:08,187
and the hospital director
received the totals.

768
01:00:08,271 --> 01:00:10,398
Why did this person post
February's report?

769
01:00:11,274 --> 01:00:12,567
It's from two months ago.

770
01:00:12,650 --> 01:00:13,901
Could it be

771
01:00:13,985 --> 01:00:16,571
that the late hospital director
gave the documents to someone here?

772
01:00:18,114 --> 01:00:20,992
Along with his ID and password so that
this can be posted after his death?

773
01:00:23,494 --> 01:00:24,787
We are checking with Accounting.

774
01:00:24,871 --> 01:00:27,081
They are the ones
who collect data and generate reports.

775
01:00:27,165 --> 01:00:28,541
It probably leaked from there.

776
01:00:29,751 --> 01:00:31,002
Check the IT Department as well.

777
01:00:31,502 --> 01:00:34,631
Accounting works with the numbers,
but IT prints the reports out.

778
01:00:34,714 --> 01:00:36,924
That's the best place to get ledgers.

779
01:00:37,759 --> 01:00:39,260
But why the one from two months ago?

780
01:00:39,344 --> 01:00:40,970
I doubt it's all that meaningful.

781
01:00:41,054 --> 01:00:44,015
The departments being relocated
were always in the red.

782
01:00:44,098 --> 01:00:47,435
I guess the person who posted it
only had that month's.

783
01:00:49,145 --> 01:00:52,815
Someone who was particularly close
to Director Lee Bo-hun…

784
01:00:52,899 --> 01:00:56,527
I'll see if anyone requested material
from the Accounting or IT Department.

785
01:00:56,611 --> 01:00:58,446
Let's focus on those
who are being relocated.

786
01:00:58,529 --> 01:01:01,741
And among them…
What time was it posted again?

787
01:01:01,824 --> 01:01:03,451
This morning at 6:54 a.m.

788
01:01:03,534 --> 01:01:06,037
Check everyone who went in and out
of room 307 around that time.

789
01:01:06,120 --> 01:01:08,831
I've set it up so that you can watch
the hallway security footage.

790
01:01:08,915 --> 01:01:12,126
But since it is a sleeping room,
many people go in and out,

791
01:01:12,210 --> 01:01:13,586
so it'll take a while.

792
01:01:30,728 --> 01:01:31,646
I guess…

793
01:01:32,605 --> 01:01:34,440
you missed the director a lot.

794
01:01:38,277 --> 01:01:39,153
Follow me.

795
01:02:18,359 --> 01:02:19,444
Call the restructure team.

796
01:02:19,527 --> 01:02:20,903
From the headquarters?

797
01:02:20,987 --> 01:02:24,198
They brought this upon themselves.
I'm done playing nice.

798
01:02:24,699 --> 01:02:25,950
Yes, sir.

799
01:02:28,536 --> 01:02:31,038
GLUTTON

800
01:02:31,122 --> 01:02:35,877
NO ONE KNOWS WHO POSTED IT.
PEOPLE HAVE MIXED REACTIONS TO THE POST.

801
01:02:55,646 --> 01:02:58,566
You're the one who posted that, right?

802
01:04:05,049 --> 01:04:06,884
Don't hide behind the dead man.

803
01:04:06,968 --> 01:04:08,386
You know there's a better way.

804
01:04:08,469 --> 01:04:11,389
-How do you think he found out?
-You've given us a weapon.

805
01:04:11,472 --> 01:04:13,391
However,
it should not involve any trickery.

806
01:04:13,474 --> 01:04:14,350
How did you know?

807
01:04:14,433 --> 01:04:17,186
Are you afraid that I might tell Mr. Gu?

808
01:04:17,270 --> 01:04:20,523
You said our weapon
should not involve any trickery.

809
01:04:20,606 --> 01:04:23,693
I've seen more people get stomped on
while trying to play fair.

810
01:04:24,318 --> 01:04:28,322
You cannot put a price tag
on what I do with these hands.

811
01:04:28,406 --> 01:04:30,783
That pride kept me going.

812
01:04:30,867 --> 01:04:34,078
That's true, and now that this is out,
if we don't do anything about it,

813
01:04:34,161 --> 01:04:35,830
the president will look down on us.

814
01:04:35,913 --> 01:04:38,374
Dear respected staff
of Sangkook University Hospital,

815
01:04:38,457 --> 01:04:41,210
we will be undergoing modification
as proposed

816
01:04:41,294 --> 01:04:43,421
by the Restructure Team
from the headquarters.

817
01:04:43,504 --> 01:04:44,672
"A medical practitioner shall not consent

818
01:04:44,755 --> 01:04:46,549
to unauthorized personnel
accessing medical records."

819
01:04:46,632 --> 01:04:49,760
Punks who know nothing about medical law
are running amok,

820
01:04:49,844 --> 01:04:50,720
and you just watch?

821
01:04:50,803 --> 01:04:53,306
Why aren't you doing anything?
Why are you just watching?

822
01:04:53,389 --> 01:04:57,894
If they really are being kicked out
for not making money, we're next.

823
01:04:57,977 --> 01:04:59,520
We've never been in the black either.

824
01:04:59,604 --> 01:05:01,939
You must have offers from hospitals
lining up for you.

825
01:05:02,023 --> 01:05:04,734
I won't complain even if you fire me.

826
01:05:05,234 --> 01:05:07,236
You keep beating me to the punch.

827
01:05:07,820 --> 01:05:09,655
The dismissal of Ye Jin-woo…

828
01:05:10,615 --> 01:05:11,949
If there are two rebels,

829
01:05:12,033 --> 01:05:13,951
I should get rid of them both.
Don't you think?

830
01:05:15,620 --> 01:05:18,915
